","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2057,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/08\/allah-rahmah-prevails-wrath\/","url_meta":{"origin":17441,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Rahmah: Allah&#8217;s mercy surpasses His wrath","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen Allah completed the creation, He wrote in His book with Him upon the Throne: Verily, My mercy prevails over My wrath.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3194, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2751 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3795,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/24\/accidentally-break-fast-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":17441,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: One who accidentally breaks fast completes it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever eats or drinks forgetfully while he is fasting, let him complete his fast, for Allah has fed him and given him drink.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1933, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1155 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15419,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/gabriel-greet-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":17441,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jibreel: Angel Gabriel greets you with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to her, \u201cO Aisha, here is the Angel Gabriel to greet you with peace.\" Aisha said, \"And upon him be peace, the mercy of Allah, and His blessings. You see what I do not see.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6249,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25820,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/28\/salat-private-conversation\/","url_meta":{"origin":17441,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Believer in private conversation with Allah in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 28, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the believer in prayer is in a private conversation with his Lord. Let him not spit in front of him, nor to his right side, but rather to his left side or beneath his feet.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627